The paper deals with generating short product titles in E-Commerce, which involves natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV) techniques. Therefore, cs.CL and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of attribute tags, which falls under information retrieval (IR) and machine learning (LG) sub-categories. Finally, the paper uses a generative adversarial network (GAN) for reinforcement learning, which is a popular technique in artificial intelligence (AI) research.
